{
  "stem": "15393.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When the situation became rather dangerous again, toward the-- toward June of 1941, and one thought and saw that things are not very good, and it's very possible that the Russians may withdraw, and the Germans may, indeed, occupy us, the Russians who were going back-- some of the people, for whom my father was working, said, you must come with us.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he said no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "God knows why he said no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He just had such a-- such a-- such a feeling against these Russians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He said no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one officer came with a lorry to our home, to our house, in front of the house, brought the lorry, came in and said, here is a lorry.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I want you to put your wife, your children, and whatever belongings you can onto this lorry, and we'll drive you to Russia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the officer said, you will regret it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You will regret it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He said no, and we stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in June, 1941, we were occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my brother was a little-- he was a baby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a boy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, sure, and so was I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were schools that were open, and so I went to a school, which was fine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, may I have a drink of water?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[DRINKS] In fact, I have a little-- I had a little bit of singing voice or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Russians, as you know, the moment-- sorry-- the moment they see a bit of talent anywhere, they-- or they did, in those days anyway-- they do help it along.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I sang in the school choir, in the chorus.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
